					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">They're the same divider. In Visual2A03 they're called <em>apu_clk1</em> and <em>apu_clk2e</em> and control the OAM DMA cadence. Tracing down the exact even/odd clock used by the DPCM DMA is more of a pain, but I see <em>apu_/clk2</em> poking around it.</div>

